==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: irredentist
<hw>irredentist</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an advocate of irredentism,
especially a person in one country who advocates the incorporation of a
region in another country related historically to his country.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> irridentist.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Irreducibility</ent>⟦br⟧
